sit
Discworld player help
sit

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
sit - Change your position to sitting.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
sit
sit on the floor
sit on <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to change your position.  To sit on the floor, or to sit on
something, or to just sit down if you are sitting.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> sit
You sit down.
> sit on the floor
You sit on the floor.
> sit on table
You sit on the table.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
crouch, kneel, lie, meditate, position, stand.
.EP
